sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / KFP SDK
    participant UI as Frontend UI<br/>3000/TCP
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant ObjStore as MinIO / S3<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow<br/>Task Pod
    participant Driver as Driver<br/>(init container)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Launcher as Launcher<br/>(sidecar)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,PA: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>UI: Browse pipelines / submit run
    UI->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run record<br/>Username/Password
    API->>ObjStore: Store pipeline spec<br/>Access Key/Secret
    API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Argo: Schedule task pod

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Argo,Launcher: Per-step execution in task pod
        Argo->>Driver: Run as init container
        Driver->>MLMD: Resolve upstream inputs<br/>gRPC 8080
        Driver->>API: Cache lookup<br/>gRPC 8887
        Driver-->>Argo: Pod spec patch (strategic merge)

        Argo->>Launcher: Run alongside user container
        Launcher->>ObjStore: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTP 9000
        Launcher->>Launcher: Execute user command
        Launcher->>ObjStore: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTP 9000
        Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution results<br/>gRPC 8080
    end

    PA->>K8s: Watch Argo Workflows<br/>HTTPS 443
    PA->>API: Report workflow state<br/>gRPC 8887<br/>Projected SA Token

    Note over User,PA: Flow 2: Cache Hit (Step Skipping)

    K8s->>Cache: MutatingWebhook intercept<br/>HTTPS 8443<br/>Webhook CA
    Cache->>DB: Cache key lookup<br/>MySQL wire 3306
    Cache-->>K8s: JSON Patch response<br/>(replace container with busybox)

    Note over User,PA: Flow 3: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over K8s,API: ScheduledWorkflow Controller
        K8s->>K8s: ScheduledWorkflow CR informer
        K8s->>API: gRPC CreateRun<br/>8887/TCP<br/>Projected SA Token
        K8s->>K8s: Update ScheduledWorkflow status
    end
